- Write functional tests using pytest; place them in tests/app/.
- use conftest.py to define fixtures for the tests
- Each python module should have a separate test file.
- write unit tests for each function and class that does not call an external API
- write separate unit test for each function and class that calls an external API and mock the API calls
- write system tests for each function and class that calls an external API (no need to mock the external API)
